item.title: CVE-2024-45857|2024-09-12T14:43:45.118Z -- cleanlab -- cleanlab
item.description: Deserialization of untrusted data can occur in versions 2.4.0 or newer of the Cleanlab project, enabling a maliciously crafted datalab.pkl file to run arbitrary code on an end user’s system when the data directory is loaded.
